ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: self_evolution
ⲃⲉⲣⲥⲓⲟⲛ: "1.0.0"
ⲗⲁⲛⲅⲩⲁⲅⲉ: zig
ⲙⲟⲇⲩⲗⲉ: self_evolution

ⲥⲣⲉⲁⲧⲓⲟⲛ_ⲡⲁⲧⲧⲉⲣⲛ:
  ⲥⲟⲩⲣⲥⲉ: SystemState
  ⲧⲣⲁⲛⲥⲫⲟⲣⲙⲉⲣ: EvolutionaryAlgorithm
  ⲣⲉⲥⲩⲗⲧ: ImprovedSystem

ⲃⲉⲏⲁⲃⲓⲟⲣⲥ:
  - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: monitor_system
    ⲅⲓⲃⲉⲛ: Current system state
    ⲱⲏⲉⲛ: Monitor all .999 files for changes and performance
    ⲧⲏⲉⲛ: Return system health metrics and improvement opportunities
    ⲧⲉⲥⲧ_ⲥⲁⲥⲉⲥ:
      - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: basic_monitoring
        ⲓⲛⲡⲩⲧ: {files: ["kernel.999", "memory.999"], metrics: ["performance", "stability"]}
        ⲉⲝⲡⲉⲥⲧⲉⲇ: {health_score: 0.85, improvements: ["optimize_memory", "add_caching"]}

  - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: predict_improvements
    ⲅⲓⲃⲉⲛ: System metrics and PAS data
    ⲱⲏⲉⲛ: Apply PAS methodology to predict optimal improvements
    ⲧⲏⲉⲛ: Return prioritized improvement suggestions
    ⲧⲉⲥⲧ_ⲥⲁⲥⲉⲥ:
      - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: pas_prediction
        ⲓⲛⲡⲩⲧ: {current_complexity: "O(n²)", target: "memory.999"}
        ⲉⲝⲡⲉⲥⲧⲉⲇ: {predicted: "O(n log n)", confidence: 0.92, patterns: ["D&C", "PRE"]}

  - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: apply_evolution
    ⲅⲓⲃⲉⲛ: Improvement suggestions and safety constraints
    ⲱⲏⲉⲛ: Automatically rewrite .999 files with improvements
    ⲧⲏⲉⲛ: Return updated files and validation results
    ⲧⲉⲥⲧ_ⲥⲁⲥⲉⲥ:
      - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: safe_evolution
        ⲓⲛⲡⲩⲧ: {target: "memory.999", improvement: "add_caching", safety_level: "high"}
        ⲉⲝⲡⲉⲥⲧⲉⲇ: {updated: true, validation_passed: true, performance_gain: 1.5}

  - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: validate_changes
    ⲅⲓⲃⲉⲛ: Updated files and test suites
    ⲱⲏⲉⲛ: Run comprehensive validation on all changes
    ⲧⲏⲉⲛ: Return validation results and rollback if needed
    ⲧⲉⲥⲧ_ⲥⲁⲥⲉⲥ:
      - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: comprehensive_validation
        ⲓⲛⲡⲩⲧ: {files: ["memory.999"], tests: ["performance", "correctness", "stability"]}
        ⲉⲝⲡⲉⲥⲧⲉⲇ: {all_passed: true, performance_improved: true, no_regressions: true}

  - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: continuous_learning
    ⲅⲓⲃⲉⲛ: Evolution results and feedback
    ⲱⲏⲉⲛ: Learn from successful and failed improvements
    ⲧⲏⲉⲛ: Update PAS database and improve prediction accuracy
    ⲧⲉⲥⲧ_ⲥⲁⲥⲉⲥ:
      - ⲛⲁⲙⲉ: learning_from_success
        ⲓⲛⲡⲩⲧ: {improvement: "caching", result: "success", gain: 1.5}
        ⲉⲝⲡⲉⲥⲧⲉⲇ: {pas_updated: true, pattern_confidence: 0.95, future_predictions: "improved"}